text: Tabirqo was a king of Kush, ruling from Meroë in the first half of the 2nd century BCE. Tabirqo's name is known only from his tomb, Beg. N 9 in Meroë. ==References== Category:Kushite Monarchs Category:Tabirqo Category:2nd-century BC monarchs of Kush Category:2nd-century BC monarchs in Africa
title: Tabirqo
